<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">
        <?php echo $this->stencil->setHeadline('AIR - Adobe Integrated Runtime'); ?>
        <p><strong>Adobe Integrated Runtime</strong>, also known as <strong>AIR</strong>, is a cross-platform run-time system developed by <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Adobe Systems', 'C'); ?> for building Rich Internet applications (RIA) that can be run as desktop applications or on mobile devices, programmed using <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Adobe Flash', 'IT'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Apache Flex', 'SD'); ?> (formerly Adobe Flex), <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('HTML', 'WD'); ?>, and <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('AJAX', 'WD'); ?>.</p>
        <p>The runtime supports installable applications on <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Windows', 'OS'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Mac OS X', 'OS'); ?> and some mobile operating systems such as <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('BlackBerry OS', 'OS'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('iOS', 'OS'); ?> and <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Android', 'OS'); ?>.</p>
        <p>It also originally ran on <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Linux', 'OS'); ?>, but support was discontinued as of version 2.6 in 2011.</p>
